1
00:00:00,520 --> 00:00:01,520
Cemal.

2
00:00:02,320 --> 00:00:03,360
Yes, Mr. Haydar.

3
00:00:03,840 --> 00:00:06,360
Sadly, we reached the end of
the time we allocated for you.

4
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:07,920
What is going on?

5
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:09,920
What are you doing?

6
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:11,280
Let go.

7
00:00:11,760 --> 00:00:12,760
Let go.

8
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:14,600
Haydar.

9
00:00:15,520 --> 00:00:16,880
You are going nowhere.

10
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:19,480
Look at these walls carefully.

11
00:00:20,720 --> 00:00:22,800
We knew every inch of this place.

12
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:25,200
You will learn too.

13
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:29,080
Eylül would come hug me in fear.

14
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:32,320
I told her stories so she could sleep.

15
00:00:33,120 --> 00:00:35,680
You will answer for what you
did to my husband and family.

16
00:00:36,760 --> 00:00:39,080
One day I will catch your weakness.

17
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:43,200
Then I will be right beside you.

18
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:47,560
If your husband were a real man,
he helped others more than you.

19
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:50,440
You killed my baby.

20
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:53,159
You had my son killed.

21
00:00:53,160 --> 00:00:56,000
My baby was innocent. Not a murderer.

22
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:59,160
I thought this love would save
me from the darkness I fell into.

23
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:02,560
Turns out I moved from
one darkness into another.

24
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:05,360
From my family’s lies into yours.

25
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:08,520
I will not. I will not give up on you.

26
00:01:08,800 --> 00:01:11,239
I said let go. You are too late.

27
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,440
I will not allow you to leave.

28
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:13,880
Enough, let go now.

29
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,800
Good that I taught you to use a gun.

30
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:25,400
Leaving or shooting
makes no difference now.

31
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:28,560
Do you see what you turned me into?

32
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:31,480
You ruined everything.

33
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,200
If you do not believe, shoot me.

34
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,680
Leave me alone, stay away.

35
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,319
Mercan, listen to me.

36
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:37,840
Do not. No, be silent.

