47
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:39,399
Ateş. Ateş. Are you okay? I am so sorry.

48
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,280
What have I done? I am so sorry.

49
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:44,800
Calm down. The bullet
only grazed. Do not panic.

50
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:47,999
We have to call an ambulance right away.

51
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,000
Where is my phone?

52
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:53,719
Do not call. No hospital.
Do not call for nothing.

53
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:55,439
That is not happening.
Do not talk nonsense.

54
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:57,240
That is not happening.
I told you not to call.

55
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,880
What are you doing? Stop.

56
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:03,000
I told you no. Do not call
an ambulance or anything.

57
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:06,040
Then let us call a doctor to the house.

58
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:11,080
I said no, Mercan. I will
get in trouble with the police.

59
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:13,879
I cannot let them take you.

60
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:16,760
No doctor, no hospital.
Neither is happening.

61
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:20,120
Come here first.

62
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:29,239
Do not be ridiculous.

63
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,640
Are you refusing treatment because of me?

64
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,240
That is not happening.

65
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:46,640
Please let us go to the hospital.

66
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,799
This is not the time to think like that.

67
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,839
We might do something wrong.

68
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:56,800
It could get infected, something
could happen. Please, let us go.

69
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:04,720
My God, what have I done? What have I done?

70
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,360
Calm down.

71
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,479
I will not let anything happen to you.

72
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,160
I beg you, let us go. Please.

73
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,600
Nothing will happen to me.

74
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:28,200
Just stay calm and help me.

75
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,080
Do you hear me?

76
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,200
Bring a towel from the
bathroom, make a compress.

77
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,600
Okay.

78
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:46,880
I brought it.

79
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:51,879
Look, you are not okay.
You are in a lot of pain.

80
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,480
Please let us go to the hospital.

81
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:56,640
If you do not help a little
more, I really will not be okay.

82
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,920
I am truly very sorry.

83
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:08,199
There are painkillers inside. I will check.

84
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:10,199
I will get the first aid kit and come back.

85
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,240
Okay?

86
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,800
Why are you smiling?

87
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:23,880
I like that you are taking care of me.

88
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:27,279
Because you are injured, I…

89
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:29,400
No, Mercan.

90
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,680
Because you care.

91
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,320
I taught you that.

92
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,760
If you wanted to…

93
00:06:57,800 --> 00:07:01,920
If you wanted to, you could
have shot me right here.

94
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,920
You already did.

95
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:22,479
Sorry for being clumsy with a gun.

96
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:25,000
Next time I will focus on the target.

97
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,680
You will not.

98
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:30,760
Even this was an accident.

99
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:33,999
Anyway, is this really what
we are going to argue about?

100
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,040
Look, your bleeding is getting worse.

101
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,040
Open that door. Come on.

102
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,480
Open it.

103
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,480
Ateş.

104
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,360
Put this shirt on me.

105
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,280
What are we going to do?

106
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,000
Ateş.

107
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,920
I heard a gunshot.

108
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:56,720
Ateş.

109
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:57,960
It came from Ateş’s room.

110
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,439
Oh my God. She shot my daughter.

111
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:01,440
Mercan.

112
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:04,160
Maybe your daughter shot my son.

113
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:07,600
Get out of my way. Your
grudge and hatred are not over.

114
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,440
Ateş, are you okay?

115
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:11,520
Ateş, can you open the door?

116
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:14,400
I am calling the police. She
definitely shot my daughter.

117
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,880
Ateş would never do such a thing.

118
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,320
He would never hurt Mercan.

119
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,120
Ateş, open the door.

120
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,640
Cemal, break the door now.

121
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,640
I said break it.

122
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,999
What is going on? What is all this noise?

123
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,720
Son, we heard a gunshot. Are you okay?

124
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,840
What did you do to my daughter?

125
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,280
Where is Mercan?

126
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,520
There is no need to worry, mom.

127
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,120
I am fine.

128
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:47,680
How am I not supposed
to worry, my daughter?

129
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,080
We heard a gunshot.

130
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,800
I was cleaning the gun.

131
00:08:58,760 --> 00:08:59,800
It went off suddenly.

132
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,280
Can I come in?

133
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,360
Please.

134
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:13,080
Come on, look. There is
nothing. You saw it yourselves.

135
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,400
Let us not make this bigger.

136
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,800
Oh Müzeyyen mother, for
God’s sake, let us go.

137
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:32,200
That girl did something,
and Ateş is protecting her.

138
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,080
Come on, Müzeyyen mother.

139
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,560
Aslı, come on.

140
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,800
Oh mother, wait, wait.

141
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:01,240
Those hunter guys downstairs maybe.

142
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,400
No son, what hunters?

143
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:03,880
It probably came from the mansion.

144
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:10,560
No, no.

145
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:12,360
The sound came from the mansion. I am sure.

146
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:14,480
I do not think so, brother.

147
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:17,120
Look how many minutes have
passed. There is no movement.

148
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:19,040
I also think it did not
come from the mansion.

149
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:24,360
I will still go and check.

150
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,039
Wait son, I am coming too.

151
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:27,280
Come, come. Hold me.

152
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:29,280
I will hold you, Aunt Binnaz. Do not fall.

153
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:32,080
Mom, be careful.

154
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,080
Where are you going, Berat?

155
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:37,360
Do not interfere. You do not entertain us.

156
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,880
Brother, my mom left. Do you realize?

157
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:43,040
Are you not going after her?

158
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,920
Stay. Something might happen.

159
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,856
Do not interfere in their business.

160
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:49,280
No, no, I will go and check too.

161
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:56,360
Do not get between me and Berat, Çiçek.

162
00:10:58,560 --> 00:11:01,880
Get out of that role of the bride
who loves her husband too much.

163
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:03,760
It is not convincing.

164
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,840
Why did you not tell them?

165
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:19,320
You do not want a doctor. You
are not going to the hospital.

166
00:11:20,160 --> 00:11:21,496
At least let us treat you at home.

167
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,760
Let them help.

168
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,280
We will handle it ourselves.

169
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:29,720
First, to clean the wound…

170
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:32,040
…bring supplies from the first aid kit.

171
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,120
Please do not be stubborn.

172
00:11:33,121 --> 00:11:35,280
Look, the wound could get infected.

173
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,920
Will you shut up already?

174
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:40,760
Do not drag this out.

175
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:47,800
Sit down. Sit. Sit. Sit.

176
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:52,520
I do not care what they will do to me.

177
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,280
I am not afraid of them, okay?

178
00:11:54,520 --> 00:11:55,640
Your health comes first.

179
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:58,440
I care.

180
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:04,600
I will not let anyone
hurt you or cause you pain.

181
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:12,760
If a single strand of your hair is
harmed, I will tear the world apart.

182
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:17,200
How painful to hear that.

183
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:20,600
Because the one who
hurt me the most was you.

184
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,360
Anyway, we need to do
something for your arm.

185
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:36,720
And I cannot deal with
guilt after all this.

186
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:41,600
Can you imagine what would happen
if the people at the mansion find out?

187
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:49,560
Not only you.

188
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:55,640
Your mother would also
be destroyed by Müzeyyen.

189
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,720
Come on, do not be stubborn. Help me.

190
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,120
Haydar.

191
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:26,560
Nermin.

192
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:28,999
I heard a gunshot. Are you okay?

193
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,360
We are fine. Do not worry.

194
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:34,240
Ateş’s gun went off
while he was cleaning it.

195
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:36,600
You never know with these people.

196
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:38,760
Be careful.

197
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:42,560
I thought he shot Mercan. I was terrified.

198
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:48,200
Nermin, Müzeyyen is
dangerous. Stay away from her.

199
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:52,600
Okay, okay. Do not worry.

200
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:54,800
You need to help me.

201
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,159
You need to get me out of here, Nermin.

202
00:13:57,160 --> 00:13:59,480
What can I do, Haydar?

203
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,560
They are armed. Do you not see?

204
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:04,240
What do you mean what can you do?

205
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:05,960
Find a way. Be useful for once.

206
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:09,640
All of this is because of you, Haydar.

207
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:12,840
So do not try to dump your guilt on me.

208
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,520
Patience, my God.

209
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,920
Send Mercan to me.

210
00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:18,680
She would never hurt me.

211
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:21,080
She will find a way and get me out quickly.

212
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,840
Okay, okay.

213
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:34,240
Tahir… I will make you pay for all of this.

214
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,080
No, Ateş is lying.

215
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:44,520
He would not accidentally fire a gun.

216
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,600
I think he is lying too.

217
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:49,280
And why would he clean
his gun out of nowhere?

218
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:50,480
I will go check.

219
00:14:50,520 --> 00:14:52,080
Aslı, wait.

220
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:54,000
There is nothing. You saw it yourselves.

221
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:56,040
If something were wrong,
would he not tell us?

222
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:57,280
He would not.

223
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,840
Son, you know that very well.

224
00:15:00,920 --> 00:15:03,201
Even if his arm were torn
off, Ateş would not say a word.

225
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:05,616
Okay mom, it is none of our business.

226
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:06,640
Let us stay out of it.

227
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:08,440
I do not feel comfortable at all.

228
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:09,720
I am going to check. If needed,
I will force my way into the room.

229
00:15:09,721 --> 00:15:10,879
Mom, for God’s sake, calm down.

230
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:12,400
For God’s sake, calm down.

231
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:14,400
If something were wrong, he would tell us.

232
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:16,000
Why are we pressuring this man so much?

233
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,376
If anything happens, I will handle it.

234
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:20,400
You are not needed.

235
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:25,280
If that girl did something
to him, I will kill her.

236
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,440
I wish she did.

237
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:35,240
Then I would have a valid
reason for what I would do.

238
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,880
Ateş could never stop me.

239
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:04,680
He does not look well at all.

240
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:08,920
I am very sorry. I did
not want it to be like this.

241
00:16:16,880 --> 00:16:18,280
Do not be sad.

242
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,359
It is just a simple graze.

243
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,640
There is nothing.

244
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,440
I am actually very fine.

245
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:33,240
You are trying to reassure me,
but it really needs intervention.

246
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:36,120
I am telling the truth.

247
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,640
I knew you loved me.

248
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:48,080
But it was good to see it with my own eyes.

249
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:56,160
What am I saying, and what are you saying?

250
00:16:58,920 --> 00:17:00,600
We will manage with these for now.

251
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:12,720
Ateş, Cemal, I… open the door.

252
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:22,840
Open the door.

253
00:17:39,320 --> 00:17:41,840
Now which one of you is going
to tell me what is going on here?

254
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:44,360
Ateş.

255
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:46,080
Brother, what is this? Are you okay?

256
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:47,280
Are you okay?

257
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:48,920
What did you do to him, Mercan?

258
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:52,480
Do not exaggerate, Cemal.

259
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:54,440
It is just a graze. It was an accident.

260
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:57,040
Mercan, lock the door.

261
00:18:05,320 --> 00:18:06,896
No. Get up. We are going
to the hospital right now.

262
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,160
No. What are you going to do?

263
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:10,640
Ateş, do not be ridiculous.
This is a gunshot wound.

264
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:13,040
Get up. This is not the time
to be stubborn. We are going.

265
00:18:13,600 --> 00:18:15,320
I told him too, but he does not listen.

266
00:18:17,040 --> 00:18:17,560
Cemal.

267
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:20,240
Take care of the others.
Leave him to me, okay?

268
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:22,320
No one will find out about this.

269
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:24,496
Ateş, what am I saying,
and what are you saying?

270
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:26,136
This is a gunshot wound.
It cannot be handled here.

271
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,520
Get up. Let us go to the hospital.

272
00:18:28,760 --> 00:18:29,760
Cemal.

273
00:18:29,840 --> 00:18:30,840
I said I am not going.

274
00:18:31,760 --> 00:18:32,760
Do what I say.

275
00:18:34,640 --> 00:18:35,640
Okay.

276
00:18:35,920 --> 00:18:36,960
Fine. I will handle it.

277
00:18:38,040 --> 00:18:40,320
But no matter what, if
anything happens, let me know.

278
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:42,199
I know him. He would not say anything,

279
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,560
but don't listen to him. Tell me.

280
00:19:24,800 --> 00:19:28,960
Okay. Stop. I am wrapping it now.

281
00:19:42,040 --> 00:19:43,040
Like this.

282
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:54,120
Hold it like this.

283
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,480
Okay.

284
00:20:08,440 --> 00:20:12,080
Now I will bring you something to
eat, then you will take your medicine.

285
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:16,720
Promise.

286
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:21,680
You will not tell anyone.

287
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:25,720
Okay. I promise.

288
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:42,000
Where are they?

289
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:48,880
Zehra.

290
00:20:49,880 --> 00:20:50,880
Çiçek.

291
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:53,016
Did you not come to this
house as a bride, my daughter?

292
00:20:53,040 --> 00:20:54,520
Why are you just sitting here?

293
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:56,760
Leave me alone. Get off my back.

294
00:20:58,760 --> 00:20:59,880
Oh really.

295
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,560
Am I your servant?

296
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:04,040
I already work in the
mansion from morning to night.

297
00:21:04,080 --> 00:21:06,240
I come here, cook, set
the table, wash the dishes.

298
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:07,720
Lend a hand at least a little.

299
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:10,559
Pretend I am working
in the mansion right now.

300
00:21:10,560 --> 00:21:12,000
And you are alone here.

301
00:21:12,800 --> 00:21:14,720
Why am I pretending, Zehra? You are here.

302
00:21:14,800 --> 00:21:16,400
That is what pretending means.

303
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:18,160
But you are here. Why pretend?

304
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:19,640
Just pretend anyway.

305
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,400
What happened, dear mother?

306
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:25,959
Something happened, Tahir, well, Mr. Ateş…

307
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:28,520
…his gun went off accidentally
while he was cleaning it.

308
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:30,480
Thank God no one was hurt.

309
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:33,959
I was terrified after all this chaos.

310
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:36,200
I thought they were
going to shoot each other.

311
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:39,240
Anyway, come on, sit down.

312
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:40,400
Zehra, come here.

313
00:21:45,320 --> 00:21:47,120
I first thought it was Müzeyyen.

314
00:21:50,040 --> 00:21:52,040
That woman has no anger control.

315
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:58,200
And Ateş is not a man
who would hurt someone.

316
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:01,880
I am scared of that woman.

317
00:22:03,760 --> 00:22:04,400
You are right.

318
00:22:04,401 --> 00:22:08,999
Sins in this world always
come back to find their owner.

319
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:10,680
They do not disappear.

320
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:14,560
Müzeyyen became Haydar’s
punishment in this world.

321
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:18,280
From the first day, mother and
daughter stormed into the mansion.

322
00:22:22,280 --> 00:22:24,200
Supposedly, Zehra knew nothing.

323
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,280
I said I did not know.

324
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:27,520
What do you not believe?

325
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,440
He would not tell me.

326
00:22:34,520 --> 00:22:37,120
Enough about Müzeyyen now.

327
00:22:37,240 --> 00:22:39,400
Let us not ruin the mood. Let us eat.

328
00:22:39,520 --> 00:22:41,040
Do not let the soup get cold.

329
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:42,240
Come on, Malik.

330
00:22:42,520 --> 00:22:43,920
Come on, let us keep the mood.

331
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:45,840
What happened happened.

332
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:49,680
Çiçek.

333
00:22:52,560 --> 00:22:55,320
You are starting to
resemble my mom in cooking.

334
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:56,480
Well done.

335
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:05,840
Thank you, brother.

336
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:16,400
The soup is delicious, Çiçek.

337
00:23:16,760 --> 00:23:17,760
Bless your hands.

338
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:21,840
The taste and consistency are perfect.

339
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:24,000
Enjoy your meal.

340
00:23:36,080 --> 00:23:39,440
My wife, come on.

341
00:23:40,040 --> 00:23:41,200
Do not let the food get cold.

342
00:24:11,080 --> 00:24:13,280
What did you do upstairs?

343
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:15,320
I am not stupid.

344
00:24:15,840 --> 00:24:18,120
Ateş would not accidentally fire a gun.

345
00:24:19,560 --> 00:24:23,080
I am sick of you standing
in front of me like a thug.

346
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:25,000
Get out of my way.

347
00:24:26,120 --> 00:24:29,040
You are not going anywhere until
you tell me what happened upstairs.

348
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:40,559
Why do you interfere in
everything that does not concern you?

349
00:24:40,560 --> 00:24:43,800
Your special interest in Ateş.

350
00:24:44,520 --> 00:24:45,520
What is it to you?

351
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:47,320
Do I owe you an explanation?

352
00:24:51,520 --> 00:24:52,000
What happened?

353
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:53,240
What are you hiding?

354
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:55,920
What is going on here?

355
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:02,160
Are you okay, Ateş?

356
00:25:09,760 --> 00:25:10,880
There is no problem, right?

357
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:17,480
No.

358
00:25:18,120 --> 00:25:19,640
Even if there were, I would handle it.

359
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:25,520
Why did you come downstairs?

360
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:26,960
You were supposed to rest.

361
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:28,880
I wanted to check on you.

362
00:25:30,880 --> 00:25:31,880
I missed you immediately.

363
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:46,360
Mercan, your father wants to see you.

364
00:25:47,840 --> 00:25:51,400
It is not visiting time, but
I guess permission was given.

365
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:56,160
There is.

366
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:01,440
Good.

367
00:26:02,520 --> 00:26:03,880
Then I will come shortly.

368
00:26:06,320 --> 00:26:09,320
You can go rest too if you want.

369
00:26:10,080 --> 00:26:11,320
Thanks for thinking of me.

370
00:26:29,160 --> 00:26:29,960
Shameless.

371
00:26:30,120 --> 00:26:32,360
Brazen. All of them.

372
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:36,560
Did you see how they throw jabs?

373
00:27:11,040 --> 00:27:12,040
Dad.

374
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:14,960
Mercan.

375
00:27:15,520 --> 00:27:16,880
Mercan, are you okay, my daughter?

376
00:27:18,600 --> 00:27:20,480
I am fine. Nothing happened.

377
00:27:21,800 --> 00:27:25,440
My daughter, they could
hurt you just to hurt me.

378
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:26,920
Be careful.

379
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:33,360
I will ask you one last time.

380
00:27:34,520 --> 00:27:36,040
Is what Ateş said true?

381
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:38,840
You did not do it, did you?

382
00:27:39,360 --> 00:27:41,240
You could not have hurt those children.

383
00:27:41,840 --> 00:27:43,480
My daughter, do what I told you.

384
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:47,000
They stayed here, but we took care of them.

385
00:27:48,080 --> 00:27:49,080
Ateş is lying.

386
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:53,520
They came to prepare our end.

387
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:55,520
Everything is planned. You see it.

388
00:27:55,920 --> 00:27:57,920
First they killed your
brother. Now it is my turn.

389
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:03,080
Do you believe a man who
lied to you for months, or me?

390
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:10,560
Mercan. Are you there?

391
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:13,720
I am here.

392
00:28:14,120 --> 00:28:15,840
Stop questioning me.

393
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:19,120
Stand with your family, not those liars.

394
00:28:50,080 --> 00:28:52,880
I brought you food.

395
00:28:53,560 --> 00:28:55,320
Beef broth soup.

396
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:57,680
It will help.

397
00:29:00,080 --> 00:29:01,080
Ateş, get up.

398
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:03,480
You do not take medicine
on an empty stomach.

399
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:09,240
Ateş.

400
00:29:11,440 --> 00:29:12,440
Ateş.

401
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:14,320
Ateş, are you okay?

402
00:29:21,840 --> 00:29:22,640
Come on.

403
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:23,760
Ateş.

404
00:29:32,280 --> 00:29:33,880
You scared me so much.

405
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:37,960
No. This will not continue like this.

406
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:40,800
Listening to you from
the start was a mistake.

407
00:29:45,760 --> 00:29:46,760
Your fever is rising.

408
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:48,760
I am calling a doctor.

409
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,479
I do not care what your family says.

410
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:52,640
Let them think what they want.

411
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:00,240
Do not go.

412
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:04,960
Mercan.

413
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:11,520
Do not go, Mercan. You promised.

414
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,440
Do not leave me.

415
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:16,440
Please.

416
00:30:16,840 --> 00:30:17,920
You do not go either.

417
00:30:18,120 --> 00:30:19,600
Do not leave me either.

418
00:30:20,600 --> 00:30:21,600
Please.

419
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:24,880
Do not leave me.

420
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:33,400
I am not going.

421
00:30:39,840 --> 00:30:40,840
Your wound is bleeding.

422
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:43,320
We need to clean it.

423
00:31:11,240 --> 00:31:12,240
Get me out of here.

424
00:31:12,760 --> 00:31:14,720
Get me out. How much
longer will I stay here?

425
00:31:15,200 --> 00:31:16,680
Get me out.

426
00:31:18,360 --> 00:31:19,240
Is there no one?

427
00:31:19,241 --> 00:31:20,400
Can you not hear me?

428
00:31:21,800 --> 00:31:22,800
Get me out.

429
00:31:47,920 --> 00:31:49,080
Who is there?

430
00:31:52,360 --> 00:31:54,720
Have you lost your minds?

431
00:31:55,360 --> 00:31:58,280
You know I am here. How do you not help me?

432
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:01,120
Can you not hear me?

433
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:04,120
Get me out. Get me out.

434
00:32:10,880 --> 00:32:13,120
I am Haydar Yıldırım.

435
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:26,560
You will answer for what you have done.

436
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:10,000
87

437
00:33:19,320 --> 00:33:23,560
Brother, I am very scared.

438
00:33:29,080 --> 00:33:31,719
Do not be afraid. I am here.

439
00:33:31,720 --> 00:33:33,720
The door is locked.

440
00:33:34,080 --> 00:33:35,280
No one can get in.

441
00:33:36,080 --> 00:33:37,960
Why are we staying here?

442
00:33:38,360 --> 00:33:40,360
It is very cold and filthy.

443
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:43,240
I am hungry.

444
00:33:44,040 --> 00:33:45,040
Try to sleep.

445
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:48,160
When you sleep, you do not feel hunger.

446
00:33:48,760 --> 00:33:52,120
But when I wake up, I get hungry again.

447
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,680
I am Haydar Yıldırım.

448
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:22,440
I am Haydar Yıldırım.

449
00:34:22,720 --> 00:34:24,120
I do not die easily.

450
00:34:33,720 --> 00:34:35,680
I have never seen such stubbornness.

451
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:39,440
Why are you trying to
protect me from your family?

452
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:44,080
Would someone risk their life like this?

453
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:46,760
Mercan.

454
00:34:53,680 --> 00:34:54,960
Your fever is high.

455
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:14,520
This will help.

456
00:35:23,200 --> 00:35:24,200
Mercan.

457
00:35:24,720 --> 00:35:26,960
What is it? Do you want something?

458
00:35:27,880 --> 00:35:29,640
I love you.

459
00:35:32,160 --> 00:35:33,160
Liar.

460
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:35,280
The fault is not yours.

461
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:37,640
It is the fault of the
one who believed you.

462
00:35:48,200 --> 00:35:50,479
No. This will not work.
Your fever is not going down.

463
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:53,640
Come on. Let us wash your
face and hands in the bathroom.

464
00:36:08,560 --> 00:36:09,560
Come on.

465
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:29,040
What are you doing?

466
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:32,080
You have a fever. We need to lower it.

467
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:34,440
Come on.

468
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:11,520
Okay. It passed.

469
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:42,120
My dear mother.

470
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:47,240
Our family is slowly
growing now, is it not?

471
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:54,880
Soon there will be grandchildren.

472
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:56,336
Is that something to say now?

473
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:57,360
God forbid.

474
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:06,880
Why?

475
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:10,360
Well…

476
00:38:10,680 --> 00:38:12,560
Mother, our family is growing.

477
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:14,960
You would have such
beautiful grandchildren.

478
00:38:15,040 --> 00:38:16,200
Like your handsome son.

479
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:19,320
He is still young.

480
00:38:22,440 --> 00:38:23,440
Çiçek.

481
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:28,560
Go bring the desserts so we can eat them.

482
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:31,280
Darling.

483
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:33,400
I want less dessert.

484
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:37,280
It causes weight gain at this hour.

485
00:38:40,160 --> 00:38:44,360
My sultan, whether you gain weight or not…

486
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:46,280
You are beautiful in every way.

487
00:38:47,160 --> 00:38:48,160
My wife.

488
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:52,600
How do you know every version
of me is beautiful, brother?

489
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:54,760
It has only been a few days.

490
00:38:58,520 --> 00:38:59,520
Çiçek.

491
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:07,760
You are getting a bit too bold now.

492
00:39:14,280 --> 00:39:15,920
Stop bickering.

493
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:18,200
Çiçek, bring the desserts.

494
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,000
Thank you, my daughter.

495
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:25,560
Can you read fortunes?

496
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:32,120
Here you go, brother.

497
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:48,440
Thank you, darling.

498
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:03,040
What is this?

499
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:04,440
Why is mine different?

500
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:07,800
That is the bride’s plate.

501
00:40:09,040 --> 00:40:11,120
That is how it is. It is tradition.

502
00:40:11,600 --> 00:40:13,159
On the wedding night…

503
00:40:13,160 --> 00:40:16,319
…to show how much she loves her husband…

504
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:18,520
…the bride finishes the whole plate.

505
00:40:20,800 --> 00:40:21,800
That is our way.

506
00:40:46,600 --> 00:40:47,600
Enjoy.

507
00:41:15,080 --> 00:41:16,480
Come on.

508
00:41:18,200 --> 00:41:19,200
Come.

509
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:21,760
Almost there.

510
00:41:23,640 --> 00:41:24,720
I tired you.

511
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:51,000
Mercan.

512
00:41:55,760 --> 00:41:57,000
You love me too.

513
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:01,120
I do not anymore.

514
00:42:03,040 --> 00:42:04,040
Liar.

515
00:42:08,720 --> 00:42:09,720
Come on.

516
00:42:10,200 --> 00:42:11,200
You need to sleep.

517
